long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Focus to-do list Chrome extension with minimum distraction. We have added minimum features so that you can focus on what's important. When you start your browser just add all the tasks that you are planning to complete before you close the browser.
